ta_1: decimalplaces((factorial(7)/(factorial(4)*factorial(3)))*(p_batch^4)*((1-p_batch)^3),4)
ta_2: decimalplaces((factorial(7)/(factorial(4)*factorial(3)))*(p_batch^4)*((1-p_batch)^3) + 0.5*7*6*(p_batch^5)*((1-p_batch)^2) + 7*(p_batch^6)*(1-p_batch) + p_batch^7,4)</text>
